### Docker image archive creation

1) Go to an example shuttle project and build it. Copy the built binary to `deployer/src/builder`.

2) Change directory to `deployer/src/builder` and run: 
```bash
mv <project_binary> shuttle-service
```

3) Run:
```bash
docker build . -f Containerfile --output type=tar,dest=shuttle-service.tar
```

4) Start the deployer using the `shuttle-service` archive as a parameter for the
`--image-archive-path` flag.